            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-7 hero-content">
                    <h1 class="hero-title animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">
                        <span class="dream-neon">Discover Your Dream Career</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="hero-subtitle animate__animated animate__fadeIn animate__delay-1s">
                        Our AI-powered platform analyzes your skills and preferences to match you with 
                        the perfect career path in emerging technologies.
                    </p>
                    <div class="animate__animated animate__fadeInUp animate__delay-2s">
                        <a href="#branch-selection" class="btn btn-neon me-3">
                            <i class="fas fa-rocket me-2"></i>Get Started
                        </a>
                        <a href="#quiz-section" class="btn btn-outline-light">
                            <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap me-2"></i>Take Quiz
